# Problem Statement

Different user intents require different response styles for effectiveness.


# Prompt

Classify the user input as: emotional, technical, creative, or informational.
Select the matching response style.
Generate the response using the selected style.


#vDesign Logic

Intent classification first prevents mismatched tone and enables adaptive responses without user configuration.


